{"tid":1411423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔需要民間記者會（因為冇人會報，比人扭曲，大台效應）","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:49:55.000Z","uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"117f111340cbfd62bd229cd4b0e491d5df8a16cd","tid":1411423,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:39:25.000Z","msg":"我地個記者會就係fb ig<br />\n瘋狂打擊政府記者會信用<br />\n每日政府記者會後，準時連登開po討論<br />\nmark低政府所有重點<br />\n續個拆解<br />\n兩小時耐文宣一定要ready，fb ig散播<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以依靠紅色媒體傳播信息<br />\n只會被扭曲/淡化<br />\n一定係社交平台直接渠道<br />\n直搗廢老核心<br />\nfb多年經營，已有大量廢老ac<br />\n一定要direct channel<br />\n經任何媒體轉載，都係屈鳩我地<br />\n想像一下，CCTVB唔報好過報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96065d25fa4e42dcc0eb7d8eaba523dd9a108039","tid":1411423,"uid":33307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"7ab8d838a846b43006810ecd023c1b4812aaa35a","tid":1411423,"uid":187493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"仲FB，IG？用投影機拍片加字幕就街播啦"},{"pid":"ea2dbc36e4147b4a8dd82cd254c9e6cf067f3d4a","tid":1411423,"uid":193465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:14:28.000Z","msg":"建議: 剪好片後再用直播方式推出"},{"pid":"df3022bbdda80e51104efdf5c94373e4b6c54231","tid":1411423,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"有冇傳理系可以統籌一下<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411388</a>"},{"pid":"e3099954013250a642964c4c31161473fcfaa927","tid":1411423,"uid":132544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"我地個民間記者會唔係泛民主導又得唔得？"},{"pid":"683c5ab79d135d92aa706262ec97987e00b4cd00","tid":1411423,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s